iku/e/f/8/yuan_ef737008b2b3fb3634f1d70fef52bd28.gif\" data-snum=\"5\" href=\"https://cp1.douguo.com/upload/caiku/e/f/8/yuan_ef737008b2b3fb3634f1d70fef52bd28.gif\" rel=\"recipe_img\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none; float: left;\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://cp1.douguo.com/upload/caiku/e/f/8/200_ef737008b2b3fb3634f1d70fef52bd28.gif\" alt=\"花生酪 宝宝辅食食谱的做法图解4\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 8px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></a><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; float: left; width: 480px; min-height: 200px; overflow-wrap: break-word; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 27px; overflow: hidden;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: bold;\">步骤4</p>待浸泡完成后，剥除花生外皮，全部放入锅中。 *其实花生皮也很有营养，如果你们不注重颜值，或者觉得麻烦的话，也可以不去皮哈。</div></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 25px 0px 40px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; zoom: 1;\"><a data-origin=\"https://cp1.douguo.com/upload/caiku/d/8/9/yuan_d8fc3b83e45bb9e62d934591845143b9.gif\" data-snum=\"6\" href=\"https://cp1.douguo.com/upload/caiku/d/8/9/yuan_d8fc3b83e45bb9e62d934591845143b9.gif\" rel=\"recipe_img\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration: none; float: left;\"><img data-fr-image-pasted=\"true\" src=\"https://cp1.douguo.com/upload/caiku/d/8/9/200_d8fc3b83e45bb9e62d934591845143b9.gif\" alt=\"花生酪 宝宝辅食食谱的做法图解5\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; border-radius: 8px;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dii\"></a><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; float: left; width: 48